  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Customize high-precision characters</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Players can customize their characters by exchanging characters, costumes, weapons, actions, etc. through materials obtained through exploration or killing monsters. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The characters in the game are all high-precision models and materials, with complete skin details, striving to restore the most realistic body. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257590/extras/1920c286e04ef34fa13fe3c862a8773d.poster.avif?t=1771913442\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257590/extras/1920c286e04ef34fa13fe3c862a8773d.webm?t=1771913442\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257590/extras/1920c286e04ef34fa13fe3c862a8773d.mp4?t=1771913442\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Melee weapons and firearms combination </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Players can attack close-range enemies with melee weapons. In melee combat, they can enchant combos to achieve high damage, roll over and hit hard, charge and hit hard, etc., and can also block damage from enemies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257590/extras/9d46fd1fb3e7750d189448124d176ed7.poster.avif?t=1771913442\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257590/extras/9d46fd1fb3e7750d189448124d176ed7.webm?t=1771913442\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257590/extras/9d46fd1fb3e7750d189448124d176ed7.mp4?t=1771913442\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Delicate skin and character models</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The details of the character's skin are clearly visible, from skin wrinkles to pore texture.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257590/extras/bd79da11ba60b5096b8dac42890c4e99.avif?t=1771913442\" width=616 height=1568 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Customize high-precision characters</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Players can customize their characters by exchanging characters, costumes, weapons, actions, etc. through materials obtained through exploration or killing monsters. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The characters in the game are all high-precision models and materials, with complete skin details, striving to restore the most realistic body. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257590/extras/1920c286e04ef34fa13fe3c862a8773d.poster.avif?t=1771913442\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257590/extras/1920c286e04ef34fa13fe3c862a8773d.webm?t=1771913442\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257590/extras/1920c286e04ef34fa13fe3c862a8773d.mp4?t=1771913442\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Melee weapons and firearms combination </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Players can attack close-range enemies with melee weapons. In melee combat, they can enchant combos to achieve high damage, roll over and hit hard, charge and hit hard, etc., and can also block damage from enemies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257590/extras/9d46fd1fb3e7750d189448124d176ed7.poster.avif?t=1771913442\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257590/extras/9d46fd1fb3e7750d189448124d176ed7.webm?t=1771913442\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257590/extras/9d46fd1fb3e7750d189448124d176ed7.mp4?t=1771913442\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Delicate skin and character models</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The details of the character's skin are clearly visible, from skin wrinkles to pore texture.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257590/extras/bd79da11ba60b5096b8dac42890c4e99.avif?t=1771913442\" width=616 height=1568 /></span></p>",
